- This is FBI agent Janis Hawk,

1240
01:20:37,167 --> 01:20:39,625
badge 3-0-9-8-1-7.
I need to trace a call.

1241
01:20:39,935 --> 01:20:41,753
<i>Everyone, hi, I'm okay.</i>

1242
01:20:42,049 --> 01:20:45,381
- Where are you, baby?
- <i>I'm in New York at port authority.</i>

1243
01:20:50,594 --> 01:20:52,006
<i>I have a bus ticket.</i>

1244
01:20:55,110 --> 01:20:56,545
<i>I want to come home.</i>

1245
01:20:59,952 --> 01:21:01,385
<i>I want to come home.</i>

1246
01:21:03,970 --> 01:21:05,020
<i>I love you.</i>

1247
01:21:06,456 --> 01:21:07,737
Why are you doing this?

1248
01:21:07,906 --> 01:21:10,091
You've been accept our help
for 20 years.

1249
01:21:10,216 --> 01:21:12,617
Surely, you didn't think
that it came without a price.

1250
01:21:12,785 --> 01:21:14,745
You asked me to give you data,

1251
01:21:14,870 --> 01:21:17,450
to tell you when we were running
the experiment. That's all.

1252
01:21:17,575 --> 01:21:21,165
Killing my father, taking Annabelle,
that was never part of the deal.

1253
01:21:21,290 --> 01:21:23,238
The deal is whatever we say it is.

1254
01:21:23,363 --> 01:21:25,852
And right now
we need you to cooperate.

1255
01:21:26,301 --> 01:21:28,216
Annabelle is just insurance.

1256
01:21:28,750 --> 01:21:30,593
Let's go for a little walk,
shall we?

1257
01:21:35,224 --> 01:21:37,354
It was the ring
that kept me awake, wasn't it?

1258
01:21:37,479 --> 01:21:39,977
Some sort of
quantum entanglement device.

1259
01:21:40,145 --> 01:21:42,098
What do I know?
I'm just a middleman.

1260
01:21:42,223 --> 01:21:43,723
I think you do know.

1261
01:21:44,152 --> 01:21:47,026
I'm trying to work out why you'd cause
a blackout in the first place.

1262
01:21:47,194 --> 01:21:48,689
It doesn't matter.

1263
01:21:48,814 --> 01:21:51,322
What does is that you continue
doing what you're told.

1264
01:21:51,840 --> 01:21:53,991
And don't think
your professor can help.

1265
01:22:07,714 --> 01:22:08,714
You killed him.

1266
01:22:09,408 --> 01:22:11,136
This is your last warning.

1267
01:22:11,261 --> 01:22:14,276
Cross us again and we'll start
shipping Annabelle back to you,

1268
01:22:14,401 --> 01:22:15,663
piece by piece.

1269
01:22:22,852 --> 01:22:24,105
I'm calling your bluff.

1270
01:22:24,779 --> 01:22:25,879
You need me.

1271
01:22:27,514 --> 01:22:30,064
Otherwise, I wouldn't be alive
right now.

1272
01:22:34,904 --> 01:22:37,326
I want to talk to the people
pulling the strings.

1273
01:22:37,494 --> 01:22:40,204
- That's not gonna happen.
- See, I think it will,

1274
01:22:40,373 --> 01:22:42,831
'cause I'm sending them a message.
And the message...

1275
01:22:44,418 --> 01:22:45,334
is you.

1276
01:22:46,966 --> 01:22:49,630
You have no idea what you're doing!

1277
01:22:49,798 --> 01:22:53,426
Sure I do.
I'm cutting out the middleman.

1278
01:22:55,763 --> 01:22:58,055
Too bad about your emphysema.
It's gonna make this...

1279
01:22:59,802 --> 01:23:01,309
so easy.

1280
01:23:01,818 --> 01:23:04,163
Your cardiac output is starving

1281
01:23:04,935 --> 01:23:07,271
Your heart and brain...

1282
01:23:08,152 --> 01:23:09,567
of valuable oxygen.

1283
01:23:10,699 --> 01:23:11,527
Finally...

1284
01:23:13,476 --> 01:23:14,864
cardiac arrest.

1285
01:23:17,615 --> 01:23:19,285
The bruises on your chest.

1286
01:23:19,454 --> 01:23:20,454
Just my...

1287
01:23:21,344 --> 01:23:23,205
futile attempt at CPR.

1288
01:23:31,582 --> 01:23:33,182
This is for my father.

1289
01:23:33,840 --> 01:23:35,301
You pathetic son of a bitch.

1290
01:23:38,931 --> 01:23:40,831
I never get pushed around...

1291
01:23:43,024 --> 01:23:44,552
and i always get even.

